INSERT INTO comments (user_id, commenter_name, community_board_id, comment_body) VALUES
(1,'nickolaus dymaikvi', 1, 'I recommend checking out neighborhoods near the downtown area.'),
(2,'JuliaAndrews', 1, 'Looking for a new recipe to try? How about a delicious and healthy Quinoa Salad with roasted vegetables? It is packed with flavor and easy to make. Let me know if you had like the recipe!'),
(3,'NguyenTran', 2, 'Bạn có thể tìm kiếm trên các trang web như Idealista hoặc Fotocasa.'),
(4,'MaryKIm', 2, 'If you need help with the book, I can recommend you a good books..'),
(5,'DaveLee', 1, 'I completely understand feeling tired of making the same meals. One of my favorite recipes to share is a mouthwatering Chicken Alfredo Pasta. It is creamy, savory, and always a hit. If you are interested, I can provide you with the detailed recipe.'),
(6,'EricDubois', 1, 'If youre in the mood for something different, I highly recommend trying a homemade Margherita Pizza. It is a classic Italian recipe with a thin, crispy crust topped with fresh tomatoes, mozzarella cheese, and basil leaves. Let me know if you would like the recipe!'),
(7,'Edgy',1, 'I have recently discovered a fantastic recipe for Thai Red Curry with vegetables and tofu. It is a burst of flavors and perfect for those who enjoy spicy dishes. If you are interested, I had be happy to share the recipe with you!'),
(8,'Mina', 3, 'Pour trouver une maison à louer, je vous conseille de chercher sur Leboncoin ou PAP.'),
(9,'Dilruba', 2, '¡Claro! Te recomendaría leer "Cien años de soledad" de Gabriel García Márquez. Es una novela épica llena de realismo mágico que te transportará a un mundo fascinante.'),
(10,'Nikesh', 2, 'Si te gustan los thrillers, te recomiendo "La sombra del viento" de Carlos Ruiz Zafón. Es una historia misteriosa y cautivadora ambientada en la Barcelona de posguerra.'),
(11,'Lennie', 2, 'Si prefieres la ciencia ficción, te sugiero leer "Dune" de Frank Herbert. Es una obra maestra del género con un universo vasto y personajes memorables.'),
(12,'JD', 1, 'I know the feeling of wanting to switch things up in the kitchen. How about trying a flavorful and comforting Butternut Squash Soup? It is easy to make and perfect for chilly evenings. Let me know if you would like the recipe!'),
(13,'Carlos', 2, 'Una opción interesante es "El alquimista" de Paulo Coelho. Esta novela te invita a reflexionar sobre el sentido de la vida y perseguir tus sueños.'),
(13,'Carlos', 2, 'Si buscas una novela histórica apasionante, te recomiendo "Los pilares de la Tierra" de Ken Follett. Ambientada en la Edad Media, esta obra te sumergirá en intrigas y construcción de catedrales.'),
(14, 'MariaTon', 3, 'Absolutely! To start practicing yoga at home, I recommend finding a quiet and comfortable space where you can relax. You can follow online tutorials for beginners and start with simple poses like Downward Dog and Warrior Pose. Remember to focus on your breath and listen to your body. Happy practicing!'),
(15, 'jacksonwang', 4, 'Exploring new hobbies is always exciting! If you are looking for a creative outlet, you could try painting, drawing, or even pottery. If you enjoy being active, consider hiking, cycling, or dancing. If you prefer a more relaxing hobby, you could try gardening or reading. The possibilities are endless, so choose something that sparks your interest and brings you joy!'),
(16, 'AyeshaKhan', 3, 'Welcome to the world of yoga! For beginners at home, it is important to start slowly and listen to your body. You can begin with short sessions of 10 to 15 minutes and gradually increase the duration. Following guided videos or using yoga apps can help you learn the poses correctly. Remember to stretch and breathe deeply. Happy practicing!'),
(17,'RhulaNadu', 3, 'Je suis ravi que vous souhaitiez essayer le yoga à la maison! Pour les débutants, je recommande de commencer par des séances de yoga doux et d apprendre les bases des postures de base. Vous pouvez également investir dans un tapis de yoga confortable et utiliser des accessoires tels que des blocs et des sangles pour vous aider dans les poses. N oubliez pas découter votre corps et de pratiquer régulièrement. Bonne pratique!'),
(18,'Aamir Kapoor', 3, 'Le yoga à la maison peut être une expérience merveilleuse ! Pour les débutants, je suggère de commencer par des vidéos de yoga pour débutants disponibles en ligne. Cela vous guidera à travers des séances simples et vous aidera à comprendre les bases. Assurez-vous de créer un espace tranquille, d avoir un tapis de yoga confortable et de pratiquer régulièrement pour profiter pleinement des bienfaits du yoga. Bonne pratique!'),
(19,'Dan Mazzili', 3, 'Félicitations pour votre décision de commencer le yoga à la maison ! Pour les débutants, je recommande de commencer par des postures de base telles que la posture de l arbre, le chat-vache et le guerrier. Vous pouvez également essayer la méditation et la respiration profonde pour vous détendre davantage. L important est de pratiquer régulièrement et d être patient avec vous-même. Profitez de votre pratique de yoga à la maison!'),
(20,'Johannes Bauer', 4, 'Finding a new hobby can be a great way to spend your free time! Have you ever considered learning a musical instrument? Playing the guitar, piano, or even the ukulele can be both fun and rewarding. If you are into crafting, you might enjoy knitting, sewing, or even woodworking. Do not be afraid to explore different hobbies until you find the one that truly captivates you!'),
(13,'Carlos', 4, 'It is wonderful that you are looking for a new hobby! How about trying your hand at cooking or baking? Experimenting with new recipes and flavors can be both enjoyable and delicious. If you are interested in wellness, you could explore yoga, meditation, or even start a journaling practice. Do not hesitate to try something completely new and step out of your comfort zone!'),
(15,'jacksonwang', 4, 'When it comes to hobbies, the possibilities are endless! If you are into arts and crafts, you might enjoy painting, origami, or even calligraphy. If you are a nature lover, consider birdwatching, gardening, or photography. For those who love learning, exploring a new language, playing chess, or solving puzzles could be exciting. Remember, hobbies are about having fun and discovering new passions!'),
(4,'MaryKIm', 4, 'Finding a new hobby can be a thrilling adventure! If you enjoy being active, you could try hiking, rock climbing, or even martial arts. If you are a fan of storytelling, writing short stories or starting a blog could be fulfilling. For those who appreciate the arts, learning to play a musical instrument, attending art classes, or visiting museums can be inspiring. Embrace your interests and dive into a new hobby with enthusiasm!');
